{"tid":1913170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"備戰立法會地區直選：75%投票率最理想 民主派各區有意出戰名單（截至3月6日)","createTime":"2020-03-06T14:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T16:11:27.000Z","uid":210495,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed57183c976c9c556c8807217913d31bf4f2432","tid":1913170,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"總結：<br />\n九東：<strong>黃之鋒 梁凱晴</strong>／<ins>譚文豪</ins>／<em>胡志偉或莫嘉嫻</em>／快必<br />\n港島：楊雪盈／<strong>羅冠聰</strong>／挑機講師黎明／<ins>鄭達鴻 (丹拿區區議員)</ins>／<em>許智峯</em><br />\n九西：<strong>劉小麗</strong>／施安娜／黃毓民／張崑陽 (大專學界國際事務代表團前發言人) ／ <ins>余德寶 (油尖旺區議會副主席)</ins> / <em>袁海文或黃碧雲</em><br />\n新東：慢必／<strong>立場姐姐何桂藍</strong>／長毛／<ins>楊岳橋</ins>／郭永健 (工黨)／<em>林卓廷</em><br />\n新西：<ins>郭家麒</ins>／吳敏兒 趙恩來 (工黨)／<em>尹兆堅</em>／<strong>朱凱廸</strong><br />\n超區：<strong>岑敖暉</strong>／<ins>黃文萱 (第一城區議員)</ins>／<em>鄺俊宇／涂謹申</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>盛傳朱凱廸一拖六各區參選名單</strong><br />\n<ins>公民黨</ins><br />\n<em>民主黨</em><br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷：75%投票率最理想<br />\n他又明言今次選戰跟過去最大分別，是選民早早有份充權話事，與其說參選人要奪取過半議席，其實更是選民的集體目標。參考上年區選數據，他估計立會選舉需超越區選時71.23%的投票率，「<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最理想係有75%，目標係九東3席、九西4席、港島4席、新西6席，新東就坐6望7</span></span></strong>，想做得到，就係每個選民嘅責任。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200305/FKHHZHJY5FXODK6BVYDR2ZHXNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200305%2FFKHHZHJY5FXODK6BVYDR2ZHXNA%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnMg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=6eb76f5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200305%2FFKHHZHJY5FXODK6BVYDR2ZHXNA%2F&h=3568700e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200305/FKHHZHJY5FXODK6BVYDR2ZHXNA/</a>"},{"pid":"7aee8697a9e54d73a16199c94c1dafb0643c9896","tid":1913170,"uid":116198,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"黎明獨立用大陸人身份界藍絲票啦<br />\n靜係識屌黃絲<br />\n<br />\n毓民收山啦 私怨撚"},{"pid":"7a559c2fb3558c35a750b6e80f37b14ef3ebbe5b","tid":1913170,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aee8697a9e54d73a16199c94c1dafb0643c9896","tid":1913170,"uid":116198,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"黎明獨立用大陸人身份界藍絲票啦<br />\n靜係識屌黃絲<br />\n<br />\n毓民收山啦 私怨撚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:55:51.000Z","msg":"咪初選囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7b597b7b9252c0a320a1ab93e4d74405d1b58b","tid":1913170,"uid":27458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"黃毓民都民主派？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129698b44cf8ee4fe4d08f6c9505654f97992ab6","tid":1913170,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:18:07.000Z","msg":"黃店手足入入嚟 登記完飲食界個人票 仲差一步！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1904542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1904542</a><br />\n<br />\n[[尚欠三千]] 工程同建測規園界，差3000手足趕走盧偉國同謝偉銓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1903176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1903176</a><br />\n<br />\n做緊老細嘅你入一入黎 我比張進出口界嘅選票你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1903067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1903067</a><br />\n<br />\n做網店嘅入一入嚟 登記做功能組民選民 即時有票踢走黃定光<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdzxwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdzxwS</a>"},{"pid":"4aec9fce86b4fc4ebc31bfbfdb8160907627ee7c","tid":1913170,"uid":72713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"毓民有話出咩？"},{"pid":"2b823eb8260ec120b0d8c83bd4476432109efeb3","tid":1913170,"uid":101392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4aec9fce86b4fc4ebc31bfbfdb8160907627ee7c","tid":1913170,"uid":72713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:19:25.000Z","msg":"毓民有話出咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"雖然我都唔太鍾意佢<br />\n但公道講 佢應該唔出<br